  TaN lun7 Teng-lan5 e5 tai7-chi3, chiu7-si7 ki3-chai3 ti7 Jit8-ki3-kou3-su7 ji7-chap8-si3-hau3 e5 chheh nih8. Chiau3 hit pun2 sou2-ki3--e5, si7 kong2, Han3-tiau5 u7 chit8-e5 Teng-lan5, tui3 soe3-han3 pe7-bu2 chiu7 ke3-ong2; sou2-i2 kau3 toa7-han3 siuN7 beh iu2-hau3 pe7-bu2, kho2-sioh hau3 boe7 tioh8. Na7-si7 Teng-lan5 siuN7 pe7-bu2 khu-lo5 hoai5-phau7 e5 un; chiu7 khek chha5-siong7 lai5 hok8-sai7--i, chhin-chhiuN7 hok8-sai7 oah8--e5 chit8 iuN7; i-e5 bou2 chit8-e5 kau3 ku2, chiu7 bo5 keng3 e5 sim; eng7 chiam lai5 ui chha5-siong7 e5 chng2-thau5-a2, chiu7 u7 huih lau5 chhut, chhin-chhiuN7 oah8 lang5 chit8-poaN-iuN7. Teng-lan5 m7-chai chit-e5 tai7-chi3, put-ko3 khoaN3-kiN3 chha5-siong7 bak8-chiu tiong teh lau5 bak8-sai2; chiu7 khi3 mng7 i-e5 bou2 khoaN3 si7 in-ui7 sim2-mih8 ian5-kou3, chiah oe7 chai si7 in-ui7 i-e5 bou2 eng7 chiam lai5 ui--i. Teng-lan5 siu7-khi3, sui5-si5 chiong i-e5 bou2 pang3-sak li5--khi3. TaN chiu7 hit pun2 chheh sou2 ki3-chai3 e5 kou3-su7 lai5 lun7, iah8 oe7 beng5-beng5 chai si7 bo5-iaN2. In-ui7 kong2 hit-ku3, Teng-lan5 e5 bou2 eng7 chiam lai5 ui--i, an2-ni thang chai bo5 ian5-kou3 lai5 ui--i, tek-khak bo5 chit ho7 cheng5-li2; che si7 chit8 hang7. 
  Koh kong2 hit ku3, ui-liau2 oe7 lau5-huih, chhin-chhiuN7 oah8 lang5 chit8-poaN-iuN7; an2-ni thang chai oe7 lau5-huih, chiu7 u7 huih-kun; u7 huih-kun, chiu7 u7 ngou2-chong7, liok8-hu2; iah8 u7 chiau5-chng5 e5 bah-the2, chiaN5-choe3 oah8 lang5. Na7 u7-iaN2 si7 an2-ni, mih-sai2 tiaN7-tiaN7 che7 ti7 toh-teng2, boe7 tin2-tang7 boe7 choe3-siaN, ti3-kau3 hou7 Teng-lan5 e5 bou2 eng7 chiam lai5 ui--i ? Tek-khak bo5 che2 li2; che si7 nng7-hang7. 
  Koh kong2 kau3 hit ku3, Teng-lan5 m7-chai, si7 khoaN3-kiN3 chha5-siong7 bak8-chiu lau5 bak8-sai2, mng7 i-e5 bou2 chiah chai. An2-ni lan2 thang siuN7 chha5-siong7 na7 oe7 lau5-huih, iah8 oe7 lau5 bak8-sai2; chiu7 tek-khak oe7 kong2-oe7 thang tau5 Teng-lan5, mih-sai2 theng3-hau7 kau3 Teng-lan5 mng7 i-e5 bou2 chiah chai ? Chiok-kian3 bo5 che2 li2-khi3; che si7 saN-hang7. TaN m7-sai2 kong2 siuN-choe7, chiu7 chi2 saN-hang7 lai5 chhui-li2 lai5 siuN7; chiu7 thang chai beng5-beng5 si7 bo5-iaN2 bo5-chiah e5 kou3-su7. In-ui7 siat-su2 bok8-chu2 keng3 liau2 oe7 piN3-choe3 oah8 lang5, chiu7 thiN-e7 e5 lang5, si2 pe7-bu2 m7-sai2 khou2, in-ui7 si2-chha5 oe7 piN3 oah8 lang5; na7-si7 tui3 kou2-cha2 Giau5 Sun3 kau3 taN, be7-bat thiaN-kiN3 chit ho7 e5 li2, chiu7 su3-su ngou2-keng iah8 bo5 chit ho7 e5 oe7. 
  Koh kang2-kiu3 Sin-cheng Jit8-ki3-kou3-su7 e5 chheh; si7 kong2 chhu3-piN u7 chit8 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5, eng7 chng3-a2 lai5 ui Teng-lan5 in bu2 e5 chha5-siong7. An2-ni kap ku7 e5 chheh toa7 bo5 saN-tang5, piN5-piN5 si7 Jit8-ki3-kou3-su7, put-ko3 cheng-chha sin ku7 na7-tiaN7; taN chiu7 hi2 nng7 pun2 sou2 kong2--e5, iah8 si7 ka-ki7 kan-cheng3 bo5-iaN2, in-ui7 ka-ki7 saN mau5-tun2, sin-ku7 sou2 ki3-chai3--e5, boe7 siong-hu5. Chiok-kian3 m7-thang sui5-i3 sin3 bo5 he7-loh8 e5 chap8-chheh; chhin-chhiuN7 Beng7-chu2 kong2, “Chin7-sin3-su, chek-put-ju5 bu5 su.” Chiok-kian3 lang5 sou2 choe3 e5 chheh, m7-thang bo5 chim-chiok siuN7 chiu7 khi3 sin3--i. 
  Koh lun7 chiau3 lang5 e5 liu5-thoan5 sou2 kong2--e5, iah8 si7 bo5 iaN2, iau2-ku2 kong2-liau2 khah u7 oa2-li2; goa2 koh kong2 hou7-lin2 thiaN. Liu5-thoan5 chiu7-si7 kong2, Teng-lan5 pun2 tai7 put-hau3, siong5-siong5 phah i-e5 lau7-bu2; u7 chit8 jit8 Teng-lan5 ti7 soaN-teng2 chhi7 iuN5, khoaN3-kiN3 chhiu7-teng2 ou-a-bu2 ka7 thang5 chhi7 kiaN2, chap8-hun kan-khou2; chiah siuN7 kau3 i soe3-han3 e5 si5, i-e5 lau7-bu2 iah8 tek-khak chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni lai5 chhi7--i. Teh siuN7 e5 si5, oat8-thau5 koh khoaN3-kiN3 tu2-a2 siN-chhut--lai5 e5 iuN5-a2 kiaN2, siang kha choe5-choe5 kui7-loh8 ti7 i iuN5-bu2 e5 leng-piN teh chiah8-leng, sim siu7 kam2-kek, chiu7 ka-ki7 siuN7 kong2, IuN5-kiaN2 chhut-si3 chiu7 hiau2-tit kui7 i-e5 bu2, ou-a-kiaN2 khoaN3-kiN3 i-e5 bu2 kau3, chiu7 oe7 hiau2-tit hoaN-hi2 khui-chhui3 lai5 chhio3, kiah8-thau5 chhut-siaN lai5 kiaN5-le2; ui7-ho5 goa2 be7-bat chit8 pai2 kui7 goa2 e5 lau7-bu2, iah8 be7-bat chit8 pai2 chhio3-iong5 kap goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 kiaN5-le2; hoan2-tng2 khap8-tioh8 chiu7 siu7-khi3, ai3 phah chiu7 phah, ai3 me7 chiu7 me7. Chit8-si5 thian-liong5 hoat-hian7, khui-siaN ai-siong thi5-khau3, ka-ki7 oan3-hun7 kong2, Goa2 chaiN2-iuN7 oe7 khah-su ti7 khim5-siu3? Tu2-tu2 teh ai-siong thi5-khau3 e5 si5, hng7-hng7 khoaN3-kiN3 i e5 lau7-bu2 koaN7 png7 beh lai5 hou7 i chiah8, chiu7 toa7-pou7 chau2 beh khi3 ka7 i chih, i3-su3 ai3-beh heng5-hau3, m7-kaN2 siu7 i e5 lau7-bu2 e5 sang3-png7. Na7-si7 i e5 bu2 khoaN3-kiN3 Teng-lan5 toa7-pou7 chau2--lai5, ka-ki7 siuN7 tek-khak si7 Teng-lan5 siu7-khi3 i koaN7 png7 ban7 lai5 beh phah--i, chiu7 chin-kiaN, oat8-thau5 khoaN3-kiN3 sin-piN u7 chit8 e5 chui2-khut, chiu7 tio5-loh8--khi3, sin-khu sui5-si5 hoa3-choe3 chit8 te3 chha5-pang-a2. Theng3-hau7 kau3 Teng-lan5 lai5, chiu7 loh8-chui2 chhe7 bo5 lau7-bu2 e5 sin-khu, chi2 khoaN3-kiN3 chui2-tiong u7 chit8 te3 chha5-pang-a2 na7-tiaN7; chiu7 siuN7 hit-te3 chha5-pang-a2, tek-khak si7 i-e5 bu2 hoa3-sin--e5; tui3 an2-ni toa7 siaN ai-siong thi5-khau3, theh8 hit te3 chha5-pang-a2 to3-khi3 in-chhu3 hau3-keng3. Tak8-jit8 saN-tng3 beh chiah8, long2 tioh8 tai7-seng pai5 teh hau3, jian5-au7 chiah kaN2 chiah8; chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni hau3 kau3 oe7 khan huih-kun, sou2-i2 oe7 chheng-choe3 ji7-chap8-si3-hau3. Au7-lai5 e5 lang5 si7 oh8 Teng-lan5 e5 iuN7, chiah lai5 hau3 bok8-chu2. 
  Che si7 liu5-thoan5 e5 oe7. Haih-ah! Kho2-sioh chit-ho7 liu5-thoan5; thiaN-liau2 khiok-ia2 u7 khiok-chiat; kho2-sioh na7 beh kheng5 chin, long2 bo5 iaN2-chiah. In-ui7 tui3 kou2-cha2 i2-lai5, peng7-bo5 thiaN-kiN3 lang5 loh8 chui2-khut, sui5-si5 chiu7 oe7 hoa3 bo5--khi3; siat-su2 hit e5 sin-khu si7 choa2 kou5--e5, iah8 boe7 chit8 tiap-a2 ku2 iuN5 kau3-liau2, tiok8-toan3 bo5 chit-ho7 e5 cheng5-li2. 
  U7 lang5 khah u7 kang2-kiu3 chhim-siuN7, si7 kong2, Ki5-sit8 si7 Teng-lan5 siu7-khi3 i-e5 lau7-bu2 koaN7 png7 ban7 lai5, an2-ni chit8-si5 hoat siu7-khi3, u7 chho3-chhiu2 phah-si2 i-e5 lau7-bu2. Teng-lan5 khoaN3-kiN3 i-e5 lau7-bu2 i2-keng si2, chiu7 toa7 kiaN, in-ui7 chai i-e5 choe7 chin-tang7, koaN-hu2 tek-khak oe7 lai5 liah8 i khi3 oah8-oah8 heng5 kau3 si2. Sou2-i2 kin2-kin2 am3-chiN7 chiong i-e5 lau7-bu2 e si iam2-bat8 ti7 soaN-teng2, bo5 eng7 koan-kok i-khim; iah8 bo5 poaN3 lang5 sang3-chong3; sit8-chai7 choe7-siong7 ka-choe7, ou-hou ai-chai3 ! Teng-lan5 i2-keng phah si2 lau7-bu2 e5 choe7 sng3-si7 kek8 tang7; koh chaiN2-iuN7 jim2-tit hou7 lau7-bu2 e5 si kui thou5, bo5 eng7 koan-kok i-khim ah? Sit8 choe7-ok tho-thian. Koh Teng-lan5 i2-keng kiaN5 chiah-e5 kek8-tang7 e5 choe7 liau2, chiu7 ka-ki7 siuN7 kong2, Lang5 tek-khak oe7 phah-sng3 lau7-bu2 si7 goa2 hai7-si2--e5, iah8 soa3 biat8-si; in-ui7 na7 m7-si7 an2-ni, lau7-bu2 koaN7 png7 hou7 goa2 chiah8, thai3-oe7 u7 lai5 bo5 to3-khi3? Koh in-ui7 Teng-lan5 e5 put-hau3, si7-chhu3-piN chhin-chhek peng5-iu2 chiau5-chai, sou2-i2 na7 chhe7 bo5 i-e5 lau7-bu2, tek-khak boe7 the, kong2 m7-chai--tit. Ka-ki7 siuN7 sui-jian5 bu5-si put-kho2-cheng3, iau2-ku2 cheng3-lang5 phah-sng3 oe7 chhut; sou2-i2 siuN7 kau3 u7 chit-ho7 kan-khiau2 e5 hoat-tou7 thang chhut--lai5, ng3-bang7 oe7 moa5-phian3 cheng3-lang5. Sou2-i2 kong2 i si7 khoaN3-kiN3 khim5-siu3 e5 tai7-chi3, chit8-si5 thian-liong5 hoat-hian7 ai3-beh heng5-hau3; bo5-gi5 i bu2 ka-ki7 tioh8-kiaN, chiu7 thiau3 loh8-chui2 si2, soa3 hoa3-sin piN3 chit8 te3 chha5-pang-a2. TaN beh heng5-hau3, kho2-sioh hau3 boe7 tioh8, chiah chiong hit te3 pang-a2 theh8 to3-lai5, chhai7 ti7 thiaN-tiong e5 toh-teng2. Hit-jit8 ai-khau3 bo5 chiah8; au7-lai5 tak8 saN-tng3 beh chiah8, tioh8 seng pai5 teh hau3, jian5-au7 chiah kaN2 chiah8. An2-ni eng7 kau3 chit-ho7 toa7 kan-kui2 e5 ke3-chhek, thang hou7 lang5 bo5-gi5 i-e5 lau7-bu2 si7 i hai7-si2--e5; ou-hou ai-chai3! Teng-lan5 put-hau3 e5 choe7 si7 kek8-tang7, in-ui7 phah si2 lau7-bu2, kan-kui2 e5 moa5-phian3 iah8 si7 kek8-toa7, in-ui7 m7-na7 moa5-phian3 hit-si5 e5 lang5, iah8 si7 moa5-phian3 kau3 ban7-tai7 e5 peh-siN3. Kho2-sioh au7 se3-tai7 e5 lang5 put-ti-cheng5, long2 siu7 i phian3, hoaN-hi2 oh8 i tai7-put-hau3 sou2 siat-chhut e5 hoat-tou7. Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni Teng-lan5 mia5 chheng ji7-chap8-si3-hau3; lun7 chin te7-it toa7 put-hau3, lan2 e5 lang5 kiam2 thang oh8-i mah? Goa2 phah-sng3 tek-khak m7-thang. 
  In chiu7 koh kong2, Sian-siN an2-ni kong2, sit8-chai7 chin u7 li2, chiau3-lun7 Teng-lan5 si7 tai7-put-hau3. M7-ku2 au7-lai5 e5 lang5 put-ko3 si7 chit8 tiam2-sim beh ki3-liam7 na7-tiaN7; chiu7 siat-su2 chiong bok8-chu2 chhiaN2 lau5 i toh-teng2, thang hou7 choe3 kiaN2-sun e5 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 chiu7 oe7 siuN7 tui3 pe7-bu2 chou2-kong tau khi3, in-ui7 na7 bo5 eng7 bok8-chu2, kiaN-liau2 au7-lai5 soa3 long2 boe7-ki3-tit; sou2-i2 goa2 phah-sng3 boh8-tit pai3-kui7 hok8-sai7 chiu7 ho2, chhiaN2 lau5 ti7 toh-teng2 thang khoaN3, thang choe3 ki3-liam7; kiam2 u7 sim2-mih8 siong-hai7 mah? 
  Goa2 chiu7 in3 i kong2, Na7 lau5 teh, au7-lai5 tek-khak u7 siong-hai7, li2 pun2-sin na7 bo5 koh khi3 pai3--i, chiu7 li2 e5 kiaN2-sun iah8 oe7 khi3 pai3--i. In-ui7 kau3 kiaN2-sun e5 si5, khoaN3-kiN3 pat8 lang5 teh pai3, koh khoaN3-kiN3 ka-ki7 toh-teng2 u7 bok8-chu2, tek-khak u7-si5 oe7 siu7 be5-hek8, siuN7 tioh8 chhin-chhiuN7 pat8 lang5 lai5 pai3. Iah8 oe7 siuN7, na7 pai3 kaN2 bo5 siong-hai7; na7 oe7 siong-hai7, pe7-kong si7 jip8-kau3 e5 lang5, tek-khak bo5 lau5 chit-e5 mih8 ti7 toh-teng2. Sim chiu7 oe7 phah-sng3 tioh8 pai3 khah tioh8; koh in-ui7 pian7-pian7 ti7 toh-teng2, m7-sai2 lou2-lat8, chiu7 oe7 sui5-si5 khi3 pai3--i. Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni au7-lai5 e5 poe7-poan7 koh-khah siong-tiong7; sou2-i2 goa2 phah-sng3 tek-khak m7-thang lau5 teh; lau5 teh,eng2 u7 e7-kun. Chhin-chhiuN7 cheng5 ti7 E7-mng5 u7 chit8 lang5 ai3 lai5 than3 to7-li2 jip8 kau3-hoe7, iau2-ku2 thiaN kau3-hoe7 kong2 m7-thang chhai7 bok8-chu2; i-e5 sim bo5 beng5-pek8 chit e5 bok8-chu2 e5 to7-li2, phah-sng3 bok8-chu2 i2-keng hau3 chiah ku2, tek-khak u7 sin5 ti7-teh, m7-si7 chhin-chhiuN7 peng5-siong5 e5 chha5, sou2-i2 chiong kui-kham e5 bok8-chu2 it-chin7 koaN7-khi3 soaN-teng2 tai5 ti7 bong7-nih8. Che si7 hian2-beng5 u7 gi5-ngai2 khian3-sng2 e5 sim. Sou2-i2 koh bo5 joa7-ku2 tu2-tioh8 chhi3-lian7, chiu7 si7-soa7 chau2 khi3 soaN-teng2, kut8 hiah-e5 bok8-chu2 koh to3-lai5 pai3, lai5 hok8-sai7. Au7-lai5 long2 bo5 thang ng3-bang7 i koh lai5 hoan2-hoe2; in-ui7 “Kng hut-jian5 am3, hit e5 am3 si7 toa7.” Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni thang chai e7-kun tek-khak tioh8 tu5 hou7 i li7, chiah boe7 koh hoat. Tioh8 siuN7 kou2-cha2 e5 lang5 siat bok8-chu2, si7 beh hou7 lang5 ki3-liam7, m7-si7 beh hou7 lang5 pai3; iau2-ku2 au7-lai5 long2 khi3 pai3, khi3 hok8-sai7--i. Ho5-hong3 chit-si5 e5 bok8-chu2, se3-siok8 i2-keng pun2 teh hok8-sai7 keng3-pai3; kiam2 m7-si7 koh khah khoai3 be5-hek8 au7-lai5 e5 lang5, long2 khi3 pai3 khi3 hok8-sai7 i mah? Sou2-i2 tek-khak m7-thang chhiaN2 lau5 teh. Cha hian7-si5 u7 chit ho7 bok8-chu2 e5 mia5, si7 tui3 Chiu-tiau5 Bu2-ong5 tong-cheng hoat8 Tiu7-ong5 e5 si5 lai5--e5; khoaN3 Kou2-bun5 Pek-i5 liat8-toan7, hit chit8 phiN chiu7 oe7 chai. In-ui7 Siong-tiau5 e5 Tiu7-ong5 bu5-to7, Bu2-ong5 e5 pe7 Bun5-ong5, pun2 u7 i3-su3 beh khi3 cheng--i; put-heng7 Bun5-ong5 si2; Bu2-ong5 soa3 chiap Bun5-ong5 e5 sim-chi3, ai3-beh hoat8 Tiu7-ong5. Iau2-ku2 kiaN lang5 hiam5 i put-jin5, sou2-i2 eng7 chha5-pai5, sia2 Bun5-ong5 e5 mia5 chhai7 ti7 chhia tiong, ho7 choe3 Bun5-ong5; hou7 lang5 chai i-e5 cheng-hoat8 Tiu7-ong5 m7-si7 chiau3 i ka-ki7 sai-khia e5 i3-su3, si7 hong7 thian-beng7, kap soa3-chiap pe7 Bun5-ong5 e5 sim-chi3; sou2-i2 put-tek-put tioh8 cheng-hoat8 Tiu7-ong5. I siat bok8-chu2 e5 i3-su3, chiu7 si7 in-ui7 an2-ni; m7-si7 beh hou7 lang5 pai3--i, hok8-sai7--i. Kho2-sioh chit-si5 se3-siok8 saN-than3 saN-han2, long2 bo5 kang2-kiu3 kau3 hit-e5 bok8-chu2 e5 kun-goan5, si7 tui3 ta2-loh8 lai5--e5; koh chhou-siat e5 si5 u7 sim2-mih8 i3-su3, long2 bo5 siuN7 khoaN3; sui5-pian7 chiong5-siok8, ai3 hou7 lang5 hoaN-hi2. Sou2-i2 na7 khoaN3 lang5 pai3, i iah8 pai3, khoaN3 lang5 hau3, i iah8 hau3. Sou2-i2 goa2 phah-sng3 bok8-chu2 m7-na7 m7 thang hok8-sai7, iah8 m7 thang chhiaN2 lau5 ti7 toh-teng2; in-ui7 kiaN-liau2 au7-lai5 tek-khak u7 e7-kun. 
  In chiu7 koh kong2, Na7-si7 an2-ni, bok8-chu2 chiu7 long2 hoe3-bo5 mah? Bok8-chu2 na7 long2 hoe3-bo5, siat-su2 beh hau3 tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 chiah oe7 hau3 ah? Goa2 chiu7 in3 i kong2, Hau3 tioh8 eng7 chin hau3, m7-thang eng7 ke2 hau3. Ai3 kiaN5 chin hau3, tioh8 oh8 Sun3-te3 kap Cheng-chu2 e5 khoan2-sit, chiu7-si7 chin hau3. Hoan7-su7 chiau3 to7-li2, an-hun7 siu2-ki2, su7 long5 kong siong jin7-chin khi3 choe3; ti3-kau3 oe7 “iong5-beng5-seng, hian2-hu7-bo2”; che long2 si7 chin hau3. Kho2-sioh lang5 khah choe7 bo5 chit-ho7 e5 chin hau3, long2-si7 ai3 than3 hit-ho7 ke2 hau3 e5 hong-siok8; sit8-chai7 bo5 li7-ek, hoan2-tng2 u7 sun2-hai7 na7-tiaN7. 
  In chiu7 koh kong2, M7-ku2 bo5 hau3, chou2-kong oe7 iau. 
